<br>
A guard &lt;NPC&gt; entered and stood in front of her, waiting for acknowledgement. Rhia looked up to the girl and smiled.<br>
<br>
&quot;Alright, spill it.&quot;<br>
<br>
The amazon loosened up a little bit. &quot;My Queen, there is a woman at the gates, she is an amazon, and wishes to speak with you. She says her name is Solari&quot;<br>
<br>
At the mention of Solari's name, Rhiannon grinned. She remembered her from a previous meeting, and considered the woman a friend. <br>
<br>
She immediately got up and rushed out to the gate to welcome Solari to her tribe.<br>
<br>
***<br>
<br>
At the gate, Rhiannon spotted her friend and grinned. &quot;Solari! It's good to see you, athelfi. Come in and tell me what you've been up to since last we talked.&quot; <p><center> <img src = "http://user.netomia.com/angelkim/rhia.png"><br>
