 &quot;They are indeed fine horses.&quot; She said as she patted one of them. &quot;The amazons are great warriors, having great horses sweetens the pot.&quot; <br>
  She whistled for her mare to join her. As her mare trotted over, the black mane flowed gently in the breeze. Solari gently rubbed the soft muzzle and reached into her pouch for a treat. <br>
 &quot;As you see, I also own a very fine horse. She came to me when I was traveling outside the nation. Her breed is called andalusian. The breed come from a land where the people speak a language that strange, but beautiful. I learned a good bit of it on my stay there. But I will admit, that you do have good tastes in horses.&quot; Solari smiled at her friend. &quot; A trade agreement is a wise idea.&quot; <br>
  Solari listened intently as her friend spoke of the horses and trade route. She was happy to hear of new ideas and thoughts from someone so young. It made her reminise about her own youth. She continued to follow her friend through the villiage.~ <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/urhiannonmerai.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rhiannon Mer ai</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 26<br> <font color=#993300>(9/8/02 10:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm55.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.absolutely.net/hannigan/ah26.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~A Visitor~</span><hr size=1> Rhiannon led the way to the next building, a small brick affair that was set next to a spring that forked off from the river nearby. Smoke poured out of a hole in the roof. <br>
