 &quot;My friend....I have come to the decision that I would once again like to revive SCS. You offered me that postion once before and I replied that I would have to talk it over with Hippolyte. Well, I have talked it over with her. She is okay with the idea. But has some concerns as to how the land will be divided, seeing as your tribe has now claimed the mountains.&quot; She paused momentarily before continuing.... &quot; I did assure her that we could come to an agreement that everyone would be happy with. &quot;<br>
 Solari then asked where she could find a goblet of water and hid a small yawn.~<br>
